subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: With two victories in a row and four wins over all through the first 24 races of the Nextel Cup regular season, Matt Kenseth is proving week to week that he is the class of the premier Nascar series.
